divs: Sighting Details1. In my second story bedroom, on my bed talking to my husband. 2. Saw out side my window. 3. The moon. 4. Object looked like the moon that was still, out side my window. suddenly a mercury colored retangle slowly emerged from beneath the moon, then the "moon" came quickly down on the mercury retangle like a big eraser closing the "portal" and then colapsing into itself like a paper bag and disapeared. Also the "moon" was in the wrong place in the sky. 5. WOW!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! Wonder!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! 6. See above #4.
